{"tid":665556,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"對應ns完全破解，任天堂賬號條款新增停權（Ban）以及連環 Ban、連坐機制","createTime":"2018-05-15T05:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T03:02:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1c544c7f38650b542dbb128c87825c8a18ae7d","tid":665556,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"2018/05/14 22:38<br />\n來源：NintendoSwitch <br />\n任天堂賬號 Nintendo Account 使用條款更新，需要重新「已閱讀」一下。<br />\n條款新增了對停權（Ban）的相關內容，以及連環 Ban、連坐機制。<br />\n希望那些企圖鑽空子佔便宜的玩家珍惜自己的賬號，因為賬號不僅是一串串購買記錄，更是屬於你自己的一段旅程。<br />\nO網頁鏈接<br />\n條款更新：<br />\n9.2 若依本條款對您實施停權（中止）等措施，您就Nintendo Account服務及連動服務之使用、已連結您的Nintendo Account的Nintendo Account裝置之使用，及/或就與您所有用戶原創內容、購物內容、點數及優惠相關之權利之行使，將受到限制，例如使您的點數無法使用或失效。<br />\n若您的Nintendo Account與其他Nintendo Account相互有關聯，您亦可能因該其他Nintendo Account被實施停權（中止）等措施而受到上述限制。<br />\n任天堂就因停權（中止）等措施所生之任何損失或損害，不負擔任何責任。"},{"pid":"54524c8153b399090b6a248c4a731ebb5752a16d","tid":665556,"uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾任地獄，ban咪ban，怕你有牙？"},{"pid":"9cdb5e567f1b4d48aabd990d53880306a91dfa7f","tid":665556,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:27:44.000Z","msg":"唔怪得尋日再我再login"},{"pid":"63e0aad80b5f1997b2c01e8870ed70bdba24cea9","tid":665556,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b496d5486ccb6d541ec26984d63c9c45796c742f","tid":665556,"uid":164799,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"又開始專注ban 人唔做遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333a3745c7bbc92fd3adf62d8a6ce2a7f18b315c","tid":665556,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cdb5e567f1b4d48aabd990d53880306a91dfa7f","tid":665556,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201